  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Local Shared Objects Local shared objects such as Flash cookies also may be stored on your computer or device Local shared objects operate a lot like cookies but cannot be managed in the same way Depending on how local shared objects are enabled on your computer or device you may be able to manage them using software settings For information on managing Flash cookies for example see http //helpx adobe com/flash-player/kb/disable-local-shared-objects-flash html</evidence>
